# SIP (Session Initiation Protocol)
##Introduction 

SIP stands for (Session Initiation Protocol). It is a protocol that let applications easily set up outgoing and incoming voice calls, without having to manage sessions, transport-level communication, or audio record or playback directly.

## Contributor 

#### Designer contributor
 
We are searching some designer to design or suggest design of app. As of now it is consist of two activities which manages SIP credentials and calling function. 

#### Developer contributor
 
We are searching some developer, who is ready to add following functions

1. Conference Calling. 
2. DTMF signal calling.
